ACCOUNT.name: ACCOUNT
ACCOUNT.description: Accounts contain information about billing for services, while coverages contain information about insurance payors, benefits, subscribers, and members. This table contains one row for each account record in your system.

columns.name: ACCOUNT_ID
columns.description: This column stores the unique identifier for the guarantor record. This ID number may be encrypted if you have elected to use enterprise reporting�s security utility.

columns.name: ACCOUNT_NAME
columns.description: This column stores the name for the guarantor record. The name could be hidden if you have elected to use enterprise reporting�s security utility.

columns.name: CONTACT_PERSON
columns.description: The name of the person to contact for questions regarding the guarantor. This item could be hidden.

columns.name: BIRTHDATE
columns.description: The guarantor's date of birth.

columns.name: SEX
columns.description: The sex of the guarantor. This is extracted as the category abbreviation.

columns.name: IS_ACTIVE
columns.description: This column indicates whether the guarantor was active at the time of the extract.

columns.name: CITY
columns.description: The city in which the guarantor lives.

columns.name: STATE_C_NAME
columns.description: The category value of the state in which the guarantor lives.

columns.name: ZIP
columns.description: The ZIP Code area in which the guarantor lives.

columns.name: HOME_PHONE
columns.description: The guarantor�s home phone number (may contain dashes).

columns.name: ACCOUNT_TYPE_C_NAME
columns.description: Category value associated with the type of account, such as Personal/Family, Worker�s Comp, etc.

columns.name: SERV_AREA_ID
columns.description: The ID of the service area (EAF .1) to which this account belongs.

columns.name: FIN_CLASS_C_NAME
columns.description: The category value of the primary financial class of the guarantor (i.e. commercial, Medicare, self-pay, etc.)
entries: Sent to Consolidated Self-Pay Service Area

columns.name: TOTAL_BALANCE
columns.description: The total outstanding balance on the account as of the time of the extract.

columns.name: INSURANCE_BALANCE
columns.description: The amount of the insurance balance on the guarantor as of the time of the extract.

columns.name: PATIENT_BALANCE
columns.description: The amount of the self-pay balance on the account as of the time of the extract.

columns.name: LAST_INS_PMT_DATE
columns.description: The date the most recent insurance payment was received for this account before the enterprise reporting extract.

columns.name: LAST_PAT_PMT_DATE
columns.description: The date the most recent patient payment was received for this account before the enterprise reporting extract.

columns.name: LAST_PAT_PMT_AMT
columns.description: The amount of the most recent patient payment received for this account before the enterprise reporting extract.

columns.name: LAST_STMT_DATE
columns.description: The date the most recent patient statement was sent for the account.

columns.name: EPIC_ACCT_ID
columns.description: This column stores the unique identifier for the guarantor record. This field will be hidden in a public view of the ACCOUNT table.

columns.name: HOM_CLARITY_FLG_YN
columns.description: This column indicates whether the guarantor should be extracted. If the guarantor is homed it will be extracted, otherwise not: 1-extract, 0-do not extract.

columns.name: HB_BALANCE
columns.description: This value is the Hospital Billing balance on the guarantor.

columns.name: HB_PREBILL_BALANCE
columns.description: This value is the Hospital Billing prebilled balance on the account.

columns.name: HB_INSURANCE_BALAN
columns.description: This value is the Hospital Billing insurance balance on the guarantor, but excludes hospital accounts in external AR or bad debt.

columns.name: HB_SELFPAY_BALANCE
columns.description: This value is the Hospital Billing self-pay balance on the account, but excludes hospital accounts in external AR, bad debt or that have not yet been billed to self-pay.

columns.name: HB_BADDEBT_BALANCE
columns.description: This value is the Hospital Billing bad debt balance on the guarantor.

columns.name: HB_UNDISTRIB_BAL
columns.description: This value is the Hospital Billing undistributed balance on the account, but excludes hospital accounts in external AR or bad debt.

columns.name: HB_LAST_INS_PMT_DT
columns.description: This column stores the last hospital billing insurance payment date.

columns.name: HB_LAST_SP_PMT_DT
columns.description: This column stores the last hospital billing self-pay payment date.

columns.name: SBO_HSP_ACCOUNT_ID
columns.description: This column stores the unique identifier for the default hospital account of the guarantor. The item is only used in single billing office mode.

columns.name: EMPR_ID_CMT
columns.description: A free text comment that can be entered when the value that is considered to be "Other" is selected as the employer. This option is available only if your organization has chosen to link the account employer to the Employer (EEP) master file in the Facility Profile.

columns.name: PAT_REC_OF_GUAR_ID
columns.description: If the guarantor is the same person as a patient, this item contains the patient ID.

columns.name: HB_BD_SELFPAY_BAL
columns.description: Self-pay balance of accounts in bad debt that have been billed to self-pay.

columns.name: HB_BD_INSURANCE_BAL
columns.description: This column stores the total of all insurance buckets for this guarantor's hospital accounts that are in bad debt when using account-based bad debt.

columns.name: HB_BD_UNDISTRIB_BAL
columns.description: This column stores the total of all undistributed buckets for this guarantor's hospital accounts that are in bad debt when using account-based bad debt.

columns.name: COUNTY_C_NAME
columns.description: The category number for the county of the guarantor's billing address.

columns.name: COUNTRY_C_NAME
columns.description: The category number for the country of the guarantor's billing address.

columns.name: EMPY_STAT_C_NAME
columns.description: The category number for the guarantor's employment status.

columns.name: GUAR_EMP_CNTRY_C_NAME
columns.description: The category number for the country of the guarantor's employer.

columns.name: GUAR_VERIF_ID
columns.description: The verification record of the guarantor.

columns.name: ACCT_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier for the account record.

columns.name: LAST_BILLED_AMT
columns.description: Last statement's billed amount

columns.name: LAST_INS_BAL
columns.description: Last statement's insurance amount

columns.name: LAST_CLAIM_DATE
columns.description: Last date the claim was produced

columns.name: FOL_UP_LAST_LET_DT
columns.description: Date the last follow-up letter was sent.

columns.name: UNDIST_CREDIT_BAL
columns.description: Total account undistributed credit balance

columns.name: UNDIST_INS_CR_BAL
columns.description: Account undistributed credit balance - insurance credits only.

columns.name: UNDIST_SP_CR_BAL
columns.description: Account undistributed credit balance - self-pay credits only.

columns.name: DIST_LATER_COUNT
columns.description: Number of undistributed credits that are marked as for later distribution in this account.

columns.name: STMT_HOLD_DT
columns.description: The most recent date on which the account was held from the Professional Billing (PB) statement processing.

columns.name: MOBILE_PHONE
columns.description: Mobile phone for guarantor accounts.

columns.name: PMT_PLAN_DLQ_AMT
columns.description: This is the sum of delinquent payment plan payments.

columns.name: PMT_PLAN_DUE_AMT
columns.description: This includes both the delinquent amount and the amount due for the current month.

columns.name: PMT_PLAN_PAID_AMT
columns.description: This is the total amount of the payment plan payments.

columns.name: PMT_PLAN_REMAIN_AMT
columns.description: This is the remaining amount of the payment plan.

columns.name: HB_EXT_AR_SELF_PAY_BAL
columns.description: This item stores the Hospital Billing (HB) external Accounts Receivable (AR) self-pay balance for the account.

columns.name: HB_EXT_AR_INS_BAL
columns.description: This item stores the Hospital Billing (HB) external Accounts Receivable (AR) insurance balance for the account.

columns.name: HB_EXT_AR_UNDIST_BAL
columns.description: This item stores the Hospital Billing (HB) external Accounts Receivable (AR) undistributed balance for the account.

columns.name: ADDR_CHG_USER_ID
columns.description: The user who initiated the linked address changes.

columns.name: ADDR_CHG_USER_ID_NAME
columns.description: The name of the user record. This name may be hidden.

columns.name: ADDR_CHG_INSTANT_DTTM
columns.description: The instant that the linked address change was initiated.

columns.name: ADDR_CHG_SOURCE
columns.description: The source record that initiated the linked address changes.

columns.name: PB_SELF_PAY_BAL_UPDATE_DATE
columns.description: This is updated based on changes to patient balance.

columns.name: HB_SELF_PAY_BAL_UPDATE_DATE
columns.description: This is updated based on changes to Hospital Billing (HB) self-pay balance (I EAR 20003).

merged.name: ACCOUNT_2
merged.description: Accounts contain information about billing for services, while coverages contain information about insurance payors, benefits, subscribers, and members. This table contains one row for each account record in your system. This table is the continuation of the ACCOUNT table.

merged.name: ACCOUNT_3
merged.description: Accounts contain information about billing for services, while coverages contain information about insurance payors, benefits, subscribers, and members. This table contains one row for each account record in your system.
